nodes.text: A young child inhabited Akira, a farm located on the planet Felucia during the Clone Wars. In 22 BBY, the Ohnaka Gang was extorting her home, and the villagers hired several bounty hunters to protect them. One day, she ran over to the village elder, Casiss, warning that the pirate gang was coming.
The village child was voiced by Ashley Eckstein, who also voices Ahsoka Tano in Star Wars: The Clone Wars.
